{
  "video_id": "2K1ekrZ6ej4",
  "title": "Treatment of Active TB | Infectious diseases | NCLEX-RN | Khan Academy",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 5575.0,
      "end_time": 6415.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: This is Charles Proburg."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 6415.0,
      "end_time": 8142.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: And Morgan Theiss."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8141.999999999999,
      "end_time": 10288.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: And we&#39;re going to talk on this video"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10288.0,
      "end_time": 16823.0,
      "text": "about the treatment of active tuberculosis infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16823.0,
      "end_time": 19330.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll state the obvious up front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19330.0,
      "end_time": 24012.0,
      "text": "which is the reason you want to treat somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24012.0,
      "end_time": 28152.0,
      "text": "with any infectious disease, in this case, tuberculosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28152.0,
      "end_time": 35138.0,
      "text": "is to prevent disability and death from the infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35138.0,
      "end_time": 38231.0,
      "text": "Another reason for treating infectious diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38231.0,
      "end_time": 41119.0,
      "text": "especially important with TB is to reduce"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41119.0,
      "end_time": 47089.0,
      "text": "the spread of infection to other individuals."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 47089.0,
      "end_time": 49106.0,
      "text": "The good news about the treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49106.0,
      "end_time": 52987.0,
      "text": "of active TB infection is that we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52987.0,
      "end_time": 56031.0,
      "text": "a number of drugs which have been developed"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56031.0,
      "end_time": 59059.0,
      "text": "over time that are really quite effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59059.0,
      "end_time": 61559.0,
      "text": "at treating the infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61559.0,
      "end_time": 66077.0,
      "text": "The bad news is that unlike many infectious diseases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66077.0,
      "end_time": 68936.0,
      "text": "these drugs have to be given for a fairly"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68936.0,
      "end_time": 71984.0,
      "text": "long period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 71984.0,
      "end_time": 75110.0,
      "text": "They usually have to be given in combination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 75110.0,
      "end_time": 79486.0,
      "text": "so you need multiple drugs to be effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79486.0,
      "end_time": 83122.0,
      "text": "in treating and the other bad news is"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83122.0,
      "end_time": 87872.0,
      "text": "that resistance among strains of tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87872.0,
      "end_time": 91024.0,
      "text": "is becoming a problem globally"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91024.0,
      "end_time": 92928.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going to talk about the treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92928.0,
      "end_time": 95565.0,
      "text": "of resistant organisms on another video"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95565.0,
      "end_time": 98407.0,
      "text": "because it, in itself, is quite complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98407.0,
      "end_time": 100530.0,
      "text": "but for the purpose of this video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100530.0,
      "end_time": 102439.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to talk about the treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102439.0,
      "end_time": 105808.0,
      "text": "of active TB and we&#39;re going to make the infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105808.0,
      "end_time": 107935.0,
      "text": "the most common variety."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107935.0,
      "end_time": 109805.0,
      "text": "The one that we&#39;re most likely to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109805.0,
      "end_time": 112039.0,
      "text": "and want to treat and that&#39;s an individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112039.0,
      "end_time": 115578.0,
      "text": "with pulmonary tuberculosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115578.0,
      "end_time": 117986.0,
      "text": "So, the first thing is, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 117986.0,
      "end_time": 120191.0,
      "text": "we have to diagnose the infection."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 120191.0,
      "end_time": 122071.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s assume that we&#39;ve done that."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 122071.0,
      "end_time": 125494.0,
      "text": "We know that this person has active TB"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125494.0,
      "end_time": 130363.0,
      "text": "caused by active TB in their lungs"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130363.0,
      "end_time": 134423.0,
      "text": "and we want to initiate therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134423.0,
      "end_time": 139200.0,
      "text": "For most individuals, the therapy begins"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139200.0,
      "end_time": 143572.0,
      "text": "with a combination of four drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143572.0,
      "end_time": 145329.0,
      "text": "This is assuming we don&#39;t know that this"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 145329.0,
      "end_time": 148052.0,
      "text": "is a resistant organism and the four drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148052.0,
      "end_time": 150050.0,
      "text": "that we start off with are ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 150050.0,
      "end_time": 154120.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an acronym called RIPE. R-I-P-E."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 154120.0,
      "end_time": 157654.0,
      "text": "Where the R stands for rifampin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157654.0,
      "end_time": 163856.0,
      "text": "the I stands for isoniazid or INH,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163856.0,
      "end_time": 169880.0,
      "text": "the P stands for pyrazinamide or PZA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 169880.0,
      "end_time": 174069.0,
      "text": "and the E stands for Ethambutol."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174069.0,
      "end_time": 177877.0,
      "text": "And we treat the patient with all four drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177877.0,
      "end_time": 181862.0,
      "text": "right at the outset, with the reason for that"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181862.0,
      "end_time": 185678.0,
      "text": "is anticipate to be for a two month period"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185678.0,
      "end_time": 189722.0,
      "text": "and the reason for that is we want to blast the infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 189722.0,
      "end_time": 194606.0,
      "text": "and eliminate as many of the organisms as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 194606.0,
      "end_time": 196513.0,
      "text": "as quickly as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196513.0,
      "end_time": 199771.0,
      "text": "So, these are powerful anti-tuberculosis agents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 199771.0,
      "end_time": 203977.0,
      "text": "first line agents that are aimed to kill the TB"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 203977.0,
      "end_time": 207174.0,
      "text": "as quickly as possible over that two month period."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 207174.0,
      "end_time": 209376.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: So, we&#39;re calling them bactericidal, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 209376.0,
      "end_time": 212116.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: They&#39;re bactericidal antibiotics"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 212116.0,
      "end_time": 214642.0,
      "text": "that kill the TB."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 214642.0,
      "end_time": 217806.0,
      "text": "We confirm that by doing cultures along the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217806.0,
      "end_time": 220760.0,
      "text": "but those are the antibiotics that we start with"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220760.0,
      "end_time": 224582.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s sort of the intensive phase of therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224582.0,
      "end_time": 226874.0,
      "text": "that two month period."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226874.0,
      "end_time": 231824.0,
      "text": "Then, if all goes well, we back off to just two drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 231824.0,
      "end_time": 235077.0,
      "text": "for the ensuing four months and the two drugs"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 235077.0,
      "end_time": 237644.0,
      "text": "are refampin and INH."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237644.0,
      "end_time": 239925.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s sort of the consolidation phase"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239925.0,
      "end_time": 241248.0,
      "text": "of therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241248.0,
      "end_time": 244782.0,
      "text": "We can use less drugs because we&#39;ve killed"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 244782.0,
      "end_time": 247118.0,
      "text": "the bulk of the tuberculous organisms, hopefully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 247118.0,
      "end_time": 250607.0,
      "text": "in that first two months and now we&#39;re giving"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 250607.0,
      "end_time": 253743.0,
      "text": "consolidated therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 253743.0,
      "end_time": 256165.0,
      "text": "At the end of this therapy, which is"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 256165.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260328.00000000003,
      "text": "a typical six month period, if all goes well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 260327.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263357.0,
      "text": "we do a chest x-ray at the end of therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 263357.0,
      "end_time": 267435.0,
      "text": "We determine that the chest x-ray is improved"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 267435.0,
      "end_time": 270602.0,
      "text": "from the first one that led us to the diagnosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 270602.0,
      "end_time": 274073.0,
      "text": "and that is the end of therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 274073.0,
      "end_time": 274802.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: Okay."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274802.0,
      "end_time": 277527.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: However, there are some patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 277527.0,
      "end_time": 280532.0,
      "text": "that actually, we end up needed to treat longer"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 280532.0,
      "end_time": 284392.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t have the simple pulmonary form"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 284392.0,
      "end_time": 288950.0,
      "text": "of the disease or they have some underlying problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288950.0,
      "end_time": 291539.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: So, as if six months wasn&#39;t long enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 291539.0,
      "end_time": 293950.0,
      "text": "you can actually have a longer treatment regimen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 293950.0,
      "end_time": 296026.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: Exactly."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 296026.0,
      "end_time": 299727.0,
      "text": "And sometimes the things which are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299727.0,
      "end_time": 302411.0,
      "text": "or the disorders that are often associated"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 302411.0,
      "end_time": 304282.0,
      "text": "with a longer duration of therapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304282.0,
      "end_time": 306143.0,
      "text": "is if you have more severe disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 306143.0,
      "end_time": 310138.0,
      "text": "So, for example, TB meningitis, you would"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 310138.0,
      "end_time": 313502.0,
      "text": "typically treat longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 313502.0,
      "end_time": 316555.0,
      "text": "TB infection of the bones and joint"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316555.0,
      "end_time": 319577.0,
      "text": "you would typically treat longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 319577.0,
      "end_time": 325300.0,
      "text": "So-called miliary TB, you would treat longer"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 325300.0,
      "end_time": 327919.0,
      "text": "and even pulmonary TB where there&#39;s a big cavity"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 327919.0,
      "end_time": 331695.0,
      "text": "in the lung, often will be treated longer."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 331695.0,
      "end_time": 336333.0,
      "text": "Another circumstance that yields, makes you"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 336333.0,
      "end_time": 338601.0,
      "text": "treat longer is if the patient is"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338601.0,
      "end_time": 344008.0,
      "text": "co-infected with HIV or if the patient is pregnant."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 344008.0,
      "end_time": 347324.0,
      "text": "Pregnancy creates a certain degree of immuno-suppression"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 347324.0,
      "end_time": 351995.0,
      "text": "and pregnant women are treated for longer duration&#39;s."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 351995.0,
      "end_time": 356646.0,
      "text": "Finally, patients whose cultures remain positive"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 356646.0,
      "end_time": 358258.0,
      "text": "throughout treatment, or at least,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358258.0,
      "end_time": 361787.0,
      "text": "for more than two months into treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 361787.0,
      "end_time": 363653.0,
      "text": "if they remain positive, they get treated"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 363653.0,
      "end_time": 365769.0,
      "text": "for a longer period of time"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 365769.0,
      "end_time": 369275.0,
      "text": "and patients who have a resistant organism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 369275.0,
      "end_time": 371310.0,
      "text": "which we&#39;ll talk about at another video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371310.0,
      "end_time": 376407.0,
      "text": "get treated for a longer period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 376407.0,
      "end_time": 378412.0,
      "text": "So, back to the patient that we&#39;re treating"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 378412.0,
      "end_time": 380302.0,
      "text": "just for the regular period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 380302.0,
      "end_time": 382293.0,
      "text": "for that six month interval."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 382293.0,
      "end_time": 386626.0,
      "text": "There are a couple of very important treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 386626.0,
      "end_time": 390095.0,
      "text": "protocols that you need to be aware of"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 390095.0,
      "end_time": 392790.0,
      "text": "as these patients are being managed."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 392790.0,
      "end_time": 395602.0,
      "text": "The first is, one has to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 395602.0,
      "end_time": 397257.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re taking their drug,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 397257.0,
      "end_time": 400054.0,
      "text": "so that they&#39;re compliant with their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 400054.0,
      "end_time": 400993.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: That seems like it would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 400993.0,
      "end_time": 403634.0,
      "text": "pretty hard for a patient to take all these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 403634.0,
      "end_time": 405388.0,
      "text": "four medicines and then two medicines"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 405388.0,
      "end_time": 407126.0,
      "text": "everyday for six months."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 407126.0,
      "end_time": 408450.0,
      "text": "Voiceover: Exactly."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 408450.0,
      "end_time": 411049.0,
      "text": "And so, recognizing that this is a"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 411049.0,
      "end_time": 414081.0,
      "text": "challenge for patients to take multiple medications"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 414081.0,
      "end_time": 416522.0,
      "text": "for multiple months, you need to be aware"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 416522.0,
      "end_time": 419628.0,
      "text": "of that challenge and try to make the"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 419628.0,
      "end_time": 422544.0,
      "text": "taking of the medication as easy as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 422544.0,
      "end_time": 425891.0,
      "text": "And make sure that you are observing"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 425891.0,
      "end_time": 428894.0,
      "text": "that they are taking their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 428894.0,
      "end_time": 431022.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s talk about that observing first."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 431022.0,
      "end_time": 434134.0,
      "text": "This has been a huge benefit in the management"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 434134.0,
      "end_time": 435928.0,
      "text": "of patients with TB."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 435928.0,
      "end_time": 439083.0,
      "text": "Recognizing the need, the desirability"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 439083.0,
      "end_time": 440735.0,
      "text": "and the benefit for something called"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 440735.0,
      "end_time": 444022.0,
      "text": "directly observed therapy, or DOT."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 444022.0,
      "end_time": 447409.0,
      "text": "Directly observed therapy means exactly"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 447409.0,
      "end_time": 448537.0,
      "text": "what it sounds like."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 448537.0,
      "end_time": 451694.0,
      "text": "A healthcare provider is making sure the patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 451694.0,
      "end_time": 454103.0,
      "text": "is taking their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 454103.0,
      "end_time": 456051.0,
      "text": "The reason that that&#39;s so important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456051.0,
      "end_time": 459329.0,
      "text": "is that it will yield a higher cure rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 459329.0,
      "end_time": 462154.0,
      "text": "if they are taking their medication consistently"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 462154.0,
      "end_time": 464621.0,
      "text": "and less likely that they will develop"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464621.0,
      "end_time": 466567.0,
      "text": "a resistant organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 466567.0,
      "end_time": 471564.0,
      "text": "So, DOT, directly observed therapy, is very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 471564.0,
      "end_time": 476637.0,
      "text": "The other element of assuring compliance"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 476637.0,
      "end_time": 478880.0,
      "text": "is to make it as easy as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 478880.0,
      "end_time": 481436.0,
      "text": "for the patient to take their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 481436.0,
      "end_time": 484045.0,
      "text": "Well, one strategy is, you can have them"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 484045.0,
      "end_time": 486883.0,
      "text": "take their medication three days a week"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 486883.0,
      "end_time": 489488.0,
      "text": "as opposed to every day and it appears"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 489488.0,
      "end_time": 492120.0,
      "text": "that the treatment is equally effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 492120.0,
      "end_time": 494391.0,
      "text": "so under directly observed therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 494391.0,
      "end_time": 497961.0,
      "text": "you can have them take it just three times per week."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497961.0,
      "end_time": 502666.0,
      "text": "The patients need to be encouraged constantly"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 502666.0,
      "end_time": 505115.0,
      "text": "to take their medication, underscoring"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 505115.0,
      "end_time": 508297.0,
      "text": "why it&#39;s important that they do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 508297.0,
      "end_time": 510582.0,
      "text": "There are some logistic issues that may help"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 510582.0,
      "end_time": 512282.0,
      "text": "assuring compliance."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 512282.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515692.00000000006,
      "text": "For example, if you have convenient office hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 515692.0,
      "end_time": 517944.0,
      "text": "where the patient can come and see you"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 517943.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519867.99999999994,
      "text": "after their work."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 519868.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524505.0,
      "text": "Providing incentives and enablers to patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 524505.0,
      "end_time": 526294.0,
      "text": "for taking their medication."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 526294.0,
      "end_time": 529230.0,
      "text": "For example, providing them meals"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 529230.0,
      "end_time": 531134.0,
      "text": "or giving them travel vouchers to come"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 531134.0,
      "end_time": 536192.0,
      "text": "into the clinic or to wherever you&#39;re seeing them."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 536192.0,
      "end_time": 539169.0,
      "text": "And then there are some strategies"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 539169.0,
      "end_time": 541074.0,
      "text": "for simplifying the regimes. I&#39;ve already"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 541074.0,
      "end_time": 542775.0,
      "text": "mentioned the one, which is three times"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 542775.0,
      "end_time": 544079.0,
      "text": "a week therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 544079.0,
      "end_time": 546070.0,
      "text": "There are also some combination medications"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 546070.0,
      "end_time": 548798.0,
      "text": "available in some countries that may be valuable"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 548798.0,
      "end_time": 557744.0,
      "text": "in enhancing compliance."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 557744.0,
      "end_time": 561132.0,
      "text": "So, while we&#39;re busy assuring compliance"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 561132.0,
      "end_time": 562959.0,
      "text": "when we&#39;re seeing these patients on a"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 562959.0,
      "end_time": 565966.0,
      "text": "regular basis, we&#39;re also monitoring"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 565966.0,
      "end_time": 568862.0,
      "text": "to make sure that the outcome of their infection"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 568862.0,
      "end_time": 570081.0,
      "text": "is going well."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 570081.0,
      "end_time": 572209.0,
      "text": "And so what that means is that we&#39;re"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 572209.0,
      "end_time": 575615.0,
      "text": "evaluating them clinically at regular intervals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 575615.0,
      "end_time": 581273.0,
      "text": "often every month or so, examining them."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 581273.0,
      "end_time": 584778.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re also obtaining cultures from their,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 584778.0,
      "end_time": 587860.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s pulmonary TB, from their sputum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 587860.0,
      "end_time": 590490.0,
      "text": "at monthly intervals to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 590490.0,
      "end_time": 592911.0,
      "text": "that they become culture negative"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 592911.0,
      "end_time": 596225.0,
      "text": "in the anticipated two or less months."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 596225.0,
      "end_time": 598259.0,
      "text": "If cultures aren&#39;t available, you can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 598259.0,
      "end_time": 600183.0,
      "text": "smears of their culture, but it&#39;s better"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 600183.0,
      "end_time": 602469.0,
      "text": "to get cultures when they&#39;re available."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 602469.0,
      "end_time": 606829.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s all part of monitoring."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 606829.0,
      "end_time": 609420.0,
      "text": "Another important part of monitoring patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 609420.0,
      "end_time": 611648.0,
      "text": "who are being treated for tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 611648.0,
      "end_time": 614885.0,
      "text": "is watching for side effects and we&#39;ll do those"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 614885.0,
      "end_time": 619240.0,
      "text": "for the RIPE again, for the four key antimicrobial&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 619240.0,
      "end_time": 622885.0,
      "text": "used for treating common TB infections."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 622885.0,
      "end_time": 625184.0,
      "text": "So, R again, is for refampin."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 625184.0,
      "end_time": 628830.0,
      "text": "And the main side effects to keep in mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 628830.0,
      "end_time": 633096.0,
      "text": "about refampin are that it can cause hepatitis."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 633096.0,
      "end_time": 635933.0,
      "text": "And so, if a patient develops clinical symptoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635933.0,
      "end_time": 638463.0,
      "text": "and you think maybe hepatitis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 638463.0,
      "end_time": 640047.0,
      "text": "they get jaundice, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 640047.0,
      "end_time": 642128.0,
      "text": "You have to be recognized that refampin"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 642128.0,
      "end_time": 644337.0,
      "text": "is one possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 644337.0,
      "end_time": 646256.0,
      "text": "Another side effect of refampin"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 646256.0,
      "end_time": 648212.0,
      "text": "is decreased platelet counts."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 648212.0,
      "end_time": 650842.0,
      "text": "That is thrombocytopenia and you need"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 650842.0,
      "end_time": 652413.0,
      "text": "to be aware of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 652413.0,
      "end_time": 655715.0,
      "text": "And then a very important side effect of refampin"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 655715.0,
      "end_time": 658415.0,
      "text": "is drug-to-drug interactions."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 658415.0,
      "end_time": 661219.0,
      "text": "Because refampin is a potent inducer"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 661219.0,
      "end_time": 663523.0,
      "text": "of certain enzymes in the liver,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 663523.0,
      "end_time": 667000.0,
      "text": "cytochrome P450 enzymes, there can be"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 667000.0,
      "end_time": 669038.0,
      "text": "interactions with other drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 669038.0,
      "end_time": 671167.0,
      "text": "As it is side, refampin also may color"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 671167.0,
      "end_time": 675047.0,
      "text": "secretions red, like red urine and red tears"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 675047.0,
      "end_time": 677470.0,
      "text": "that may interfere with contact lenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 677470.0,
      "end_time": 679138.0,
      "text": "but that&#39;s more of an annoyance"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 679138.0,
      "end_time": 681808.0,
      "text": "than a significant side effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 681808.0,
      "end_time": 685017.0,
      "text": "With regards to INH, or isoniazid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 685017.0,
      "end_time": 687267.0,
      "text": "the main side effects to be familiar with again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 687267.0,
      "end_time": 688657.0,
      "text": "are hepatitis."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 688657.0,
      "end_time": 691991.0,
      "text": "INH can cause hepatitis, especially in those"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 691991.0,
      "end_time": 694638.0,
      "text": "that already have a reason for having hepatitis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 694638.0,
      "end_time": 696860.0,
      "text": "for example, alcoholics."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 696860.0,
      "end_time": 702361.0,
      "text": "And isoniazid can also cause a peripheral neuropathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 702361.0,
      "end_time": 706969.0,
      "text": "Oftentimes, resulting from vitamin B6"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 706969.0,
      "end_time": 709275.0,
      "text": "or pyridoxine deficiency."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 709275.0,
      "end_time": 710545.0,
      "text": "So you can take care of that"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 710545.0,
      "end_time": 714075.0,
      "text": "by prescribing pyridoxine at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 714075.0,
      "end_time": 717811.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s especially true if the patient has poor nutrition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 717811.0,
      "end_time": 719773.0,
      "text": "an alcoholic, for example."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 719773.0,
      "end_time": 722470.0,
      "text": "You can also get neuropathy in patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 722470.0,
      "end_time": 725465.0,
      "text": "with chronic renal, who are taking INH,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 725465.0,
      "end_time": 727228.0,
      "text": "with chronic renal failure and diabetes"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 727228.0,
      "end_time": 729054.0,
      "text": "and so forth, but neuropathy is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 729054.0,
      "end_time": 730833.0,
      "text": "to keep in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 730833.0,
      "end_time": 734010.0,
      "text": "With regards to pyrazinamide, these individuals"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 734010.0,
      "end_time": 739042.0,
      "text": "may get high uric acid levels and resulting arthralgias."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 739042.0,
      "end_time": 741837.0,
      "text": "They can even get overt gout and that"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 741837.0,
      "end_time": 744942.0,
      "text": "would be a reason for stopping the pyrazinamide."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 744942.0,
      "end_time": 748819.0,
      "text": "And then finally, with regards to Ethambutol,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 748819.0,
      "end_time": 751654.0,
      "text": "patients may develop an optic neuritis"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 751654.0,
      "end_time": 754756.0,
      "text": "which can impair their vision and that would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 754756.0,
      "end_time": 757998.0,
      "text": "a reason to stop Ethambutol therapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 757998.0,
      "end_time": 760364.0,
      "text": "So, being familiar with these side effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 760364.0,
      "end_time": 763355.0,
      "text": "as you monitor the response of the patient"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 763355.0,
      "end_time": 766003.0,
      "text": "to therapy and as you monitor their compliance"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 766003.0,
      "end_time": 768151.0,
      "text": "is also an important part of the treatment"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 768151.0,
      "end_time": 778151.0,
      "text": "of active TB."
    }
  ]
}